ast.name: Interactive input
ast.comment:
An expression editor with AND/OR and braces support, primarily aimed at web search engine queries. The expression is represented as a tree, displayed to the user as an array of textboxes, colored and seeming offset to represent their position in the tree.

The leaves are supposed to be much more richer when editing in terms of UX - currently only plain text input is provided, - which is being worked on for a particular search engine example provided.

thenBody.text: This shouldn't normally happen, but still...
